name: 6 Tribal Shields - Sulaiman Tribe
description:
Sulaiman ~ (Tribe of Peace)

Tranquility dwells in the Spirit of this Tribe.
The Soil, Soul and People are blessed with lush Fertility. Stream's and eyes that glisten diamond bright.

Characteristically the members of this Tribe are of a self sustaining and farming kind.
They make full use of their resources and in return they receive abundance of every natural and ethereal kind.

Warriors of Works. Forever at Play.
